---
year: 2022
title: My thoughts on nanotechnology strategy research as an EA cause area
type: Blog post
journal: EA Forum
date: 2022-05-02
abstract: "Advanced nanotechnology might arrive in the next couple of decades and could have very positive or very negative implications for existential risk. There has been relatively little high-quality thinking on how to make the arrival of advanced nanotechnology go well, and I think there should be more work in this area."
---
